videos.description: Utah's Donnie Tillman picks the ball off and takes it the length of the floor, laying it in despite the contact.
videos.headline: Tillman gets steal then finishes and-1

videos.description: Sedrick Barefield and Tyler Rawson execute pick-and-roll to perfection, as Rawson slams it down.
videos.headline: Utah's Rawson sends it in

videos.description: Mizzou's Jordan Barnett leaps from outside the paint for the tomahawk dunk.
videos.headline: Barnett throws down vicious slam
